	<section class="article-content clearfix" itemprop="articleBody">
		<p>Persivia’s integrated platform offers Hospitals &amp; Providers with actionable information to improve clinical, financial and operational performance. With a single integration interface, Hospitals and Providers are empowered to manage clinical and financial risks with appropriate modules that caters to every hospital’s unique needs. <br /><br />What sets us apart is our innovative and trusted award winning decision support technology that empowers clinicians to optimize treatment plans for each patient, using intelligent and actionable information to improve care quality while reducing costs. The Persivia platform is an industry-leading solution for aggregating and analyzing clinical and claims data for individuals and populations, and the only patient-specific, real-time solution that supports both acute and chronic-condition management.<br /><br />Persivia’s powerful platform brings together data from disparate sources to build a longitudinal patient record enabling multiple views into all patient data eliminating discrepancies that occur with multiple vendors and enabling more accurate, real-time analytics and reporting. The information can be accessed at the point-of-care, pre-encounter or post-encounter, in order to directly and immediately drive behaviors that will improve the quality of care.<br /><br />Persivia leverages the world’s largest library of evidence-based medical knowledge to provide clinicians with real-time patient and population assessment, at the point-of-care, when it matters most. Since the platform provides immediate recommendations for care, it enables clinicians to conduct earlier patient interventions, reduce avoidable errors and improve overall health outcome.<br /><br /></p>
<h4><strong>Key modules include:</strong></h4>
<p><strong>Quality Management/Improved Outcomes</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Real-time CQM Navigator™</li>
<li>Meaningful Use (Eligible Hospital)</li>
<li>Meaningful Use (Eligible Provider)</li>
<li>Inpatient Quality Reporting</li>
<li>The Joint Commission National Quality Core Measures</li>
<li>ACO Quality Measures</li>
<li>HEDIS Quality Measures</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Care Management</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Chronic Care Management</li>
<li>Transition of Care Management</li>
<li>Network Performance</li>
<li>Disease Registries</li>
<li>Network Leakage</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Platform</strong></p>
<ul style="font-size: 12.16px; line-height: 15.808px;">
<li>Smartpath Real-time Rules</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>	</section>
	
